```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df_log = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1"]*6 + ["B2"]*6,
    "day":   [1,2,3,4,5,6]*2,
    "glucose": [
        5.0, 4.8, 4.6, 4.4, 4.2, 4.0,   # B1
        5.0, 4.9, 4.8, 4.7, 4.6, 4.5    # B2
    ],
    "lactate": [
        0.8, 0.9, 1.1, 1.3, 1.6, 1.9,   # B1
        0.8, 0.85, 0.9, 0.95, 1.0, 1.05 # B2
    ]
})
df_setting = pd.DataFrame({
    "batch": ["B1","B1","B2"],
    "ref_day": [3, 3, np.nan],    # B1Ïù¥ Ï§ëÎ≥µÏúºÎ°ú Îì§Ïñ¥ÏûàÏùå (Ïã§Î¨¥ÏóêÏÑú ÏûêÏ£º Î∞úÏÉù)
    "glc_limit": [4.5, 4.5, 4.6],
    "lac_limit": [1.2, 1.2, 1.0]
})
display(df_log, df_setting)
```

# ÌíÄÏù¥

```python
df_setting_clean = df_setting.drop_duplicates()
display(df_setting_clean)
df_merged = df_log.merge(df_setting_clean, how='left', on='batch')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['max_day'] = df_merged.groupby('batch')['day'].transform('max')
mask = np.where(
        df_merged['ref_day'].notna(), df_merged['day']==df_merged['ref_day'], df_merged['day']==df_merged['max_day']
)
display(mask)
base = (df_merged.loc[mask, ['batch','glucose']]
        .rename(columns={'glucose':'ref_glucose'}))
df_merged = df_merged.merge(base, on='batch', how='left')
display(df_merged)
df_merged['glucose_drop']=df_merged['ref_glucose']-df_merged['glucose']
df_merged['lactate_rate']=df_merged['lactate']/df_merged['glucose']
display(df_merged)
df_merged['is_risk'] = ((df_merged['day']>=df_merged['ref_day']) | (df_merged['ref_day'].isna())) & ((df_merged['glucose']<df_merged['glc_limit']) | (df_merged['lactate']>df_merged['lac_limit']))
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted=df_merged.sort_values(by=['batch','day'], ascending=[True,True])
batch_feat = df_merged_sorted.groupby('batch').agg(
    risk_cnt = ('is_risk', 'sum'),
    lask_lactate_rate = ('lactate_rate', 'last'),
    ref_glucose = ('ref_glucose','mean')
).reset_index()
display(batch_feat)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
batches = ['B1','B2']
for idx, batch in enumerate(batches):
    x = df_merged_sorted[df_merged_sorted['batch']==batch]['day']
    y = df_merged_sorted[df_merged_sorted['batch']==batch]['glucose']
    ref = df_merged_sorted[df_merged_sorted['batch']==batch]['ref_glucose'].mean()
    x_scatter = df_merged_sorted[(df_merged_sorted['batch']==batch) & (df_merged_sorted['is_risk'])]['day']
    y_scatter = df_merged_sorted[(df_merged_sorted['batch']==batch) & (df_merged_sorted['is_risk'])]['glucose']
    ax.plot(x,y)
    ax.axhline(ref, color = 'gray', linestyle='--')
    ax.scatter(x_scatter, y_scatter)
ax.grid(False)
ax.set_title("Glucose Trend with Risk Points")
ax.set_xlabel('day')
ax.set_xlabel('glucose')
plt.show()
```
